NAME :
        Simple_Shell - 

SYNOPSIS :

DESCRIPTION :

The ***main*** function creates a basic shell that continuously reads user input, 
processes commands, handles built-in commands like "exit" and "env",
executes external commands, and maintains an exit status while providing
a simple shell prompt.

